00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:09.770
How to Share and Enjoy Endless Pictures with
the KODAK Pulse Digital Frame.

00:00:09.770 --> 00:00:14.100
Want to view pictures from your computer,
cellphone, social networks, and friends and

00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:16.949
family all in one place, hassle-free?

00:00:16.949 --> 00:00:21.071
With the KODAK Pulse Digital Frame, great
shots and favorite memories are right at your

00:00:21.071 --> 00:00:22.071
fingertips.

00:00:22.071 --> 00:00:33.551
You will need KODAK Pulse Digital Frame Computer
Wireless internet Digital pictures and usb

00:00:33.551 --> 00:00:35.570
drive or memory card (optional).

00:00:35.570 --> 00:00:37.010
Step 1.

00:00:37.010 --> 00:00:39.820
Check out the KODAK Pulse Digital Frame.

00:00:39.820 --> 00:00:45.030
The Pulse comes in 7- and 10-inch models;
each features a touchscreen and Wi-Fi connectivity

00:00:45.030 --> 00:00:48.809
that makes it super easy to share and display
your photos.

00:00:48.809 --> 00:00:49.809
Step 2.

00:00:49.809 --> 00:00:51.239
Plug in your Pulse and press "Start."

00:00:51.239 --> 00:00:55.420
Then, go to "kodakpulse.com":https://www.kodakpulse.com/
on your computer and create an account to

00:00:55.420 --> 00:00:56.739
manage your frame.

00:00:56.739 --> 00:01:01.120
Select your wireless network, enter your password,
and voila!

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:04.430
Your Pulse is connected to the internet in
seconds.

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:05.430
Step 3.

00:01:05.430 --> 00:01:09.350
Create an e-mail address for your Pulse and
invite friends and family to e-mail their

00:01:09.350 --> 00:01:14.190
photos directly to your Pulse, making it a
snap to stay in touch.

00:01:14.190 --> 00:01:18.521
You can also upload pictures to the frame
from your computer's photo library, a memory

00:01:18.521 --> 00:01:21.240
card, or a USB drive.

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:22.390
Step 4.

00:01:22.390 --> 00:01:24.280
Taking photos with your cellphone?

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:28.609
Use the Pulse's e-mail address to send picture
messages right from your mobile device -- they'll

00:01:28.609 --> 00:01:32.689
be waiting on the screen for you before you
even get home.

00:01:32.689 --> 00:01:34.039
Step 5.

00:01:34.039 --> 00:01:37.159
Link your Pulse to your Facebook and KODAK
Gallery accounts.

00:01:37.159 --> 00:01:41.679
Choose exactly which pictures to send to your
frame and watch as they're displayed randomly,

00:01:41.679 --> 00:01:44.719
making every picture a new chance to relive
your favorite memories.

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:49.480
You can also link to friends' Facebook and
KODAK Gallery accounts to see their photos

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:51.650
whenever they're posted.

00:01:51.650 --> 00:01:52.840
Step 6.

00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:57.799
Get creative and make Pulse a part of your
daily life -- give faraway relatives a glimpse

00:01:57.799 --> 00:02:02.820
of home or help your friends find their style
for a night out.

00:02:02.820 --> 00:02:07.700
With the KODAK Pulse, you can instantly display
and share every moment of your life.

00:02:07.700 --> 00:02:13.780
Did you know You can e-mail pictures to the
KODAK JumboTron in Times Square in New York

00:02:13.780 --> 00:02:18.290
City -- making it the biggest Pulse Frame
in the world!

